  "text": "## Fees & Charges  \n**Q: Are there monthly fees?**\nA: No. There's no monthly maintenance fee for SmartSaver Account.  \n**Q: What fees might I be charged?**\nA: Only these optional fees:\n- International ATM withdrawal: £2.50 per withdrawal\n- International transfer: £5.00 per transfer\n- Card replacement: £15.00 (or £25 for expedited)  \n**Q: Is there an overdraft fee if I go negative?**\nA: SmartSaver doesn't offer overdraft. If you try to withdraw more than your balance, the transaction is declined (no fee, but no withdrawal).  \n**Q: What is the debit card cost?**\nA:\n- Initial card: £0\n- Replacement card: £15 (or £25 for overnight delivery)  \n---",
